<h1>About Cafe Brew</h1>

<p>At Cafe Brew, we serve freshly brewed coffee with passion and sustainability. Our mission is to bring you the finest coffee experience while caring for the planet.</p>

<p>We believe in using only ethically sourced beans, supporting local farmers, and reducing our environmental footprint with eco-friendly practices such as compostable cups and zero waste initiatives.</p>

<p>Our menu features trendy plant-based options, including oat milk lattes and vegan treats, designed to satisfy both your taste buds and your values.</p>

<p>We’re proud to foster a welcoming community space where coffee lovers and eco-conscious individuals can come together and enjoy delicious blends in a warm, sustainable environment.</p>

<p>Join us on our journey to make every cup count—for you and for the Earth.</p>
